            <title>[LU-4892] LFSCK 5: all of the OST rpcs send the MDT inode fid</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4892</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The goal of this bug is to fill in the obdo o_parent_seq and o_parent_oid and OBD_MD_FLFID for all of the RPCs that are sent to the OST, so that it can verify whether the RPC is for the correct object or not.  That would allow the OST to refuse RPCs being sent for the wrong objects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
